Package: Rfiglet
Type: Package
Title: R Bindings for figlet
Version: 1.0-0
Description: 'figlet' is a well-known command line utility
    for producing ascii logos.  The 'Rfiglet' package provides
    bindings for the figlet library to R.  Over 150 fonts are 
    available, documented in the help as well as in a demonstration
    vignette.
License: BSD 2-clause License + file LICENSE
Copyright: See Rfiglet/inst/figlet_LICENSE for files in src/figlet.
Depends:
    R (>= 2.14.0)
Imports: 
    utils
Suggests: 
    shiny,
    knitr, 
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
NeedsCompilation: yes
ByteCompile: yes
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
Authors@R: c(person("Drew", "Schmidt", role=c("aut", "cre")))
